Title: Azimut 'Alana Rose'
Description:
Length: 55ft | Guests: 6 | Cabins: 3
Discover the perfect balance of comfort and performance aboard 'Alana Rose'.
Text: 'Alana Rose' represents the pinnacle of mid-sized luxury yachting. Her sophisticated salon offers plush seating and entertainment systems, while the expertly designed galley serves delicious meals to be enjoyed in the formal dining area or alfresco on the aft deck. The three well-appointed cabins provide comfortable accommodations with premium linens and en-suite facilities.
